::Firaxis/Horn::
       Horn, despite his newfound ability to speak chose not to and so 
together they arrived at the surface.  They walk over to the crater where the 
artifact landed.  "Huh, I wonder what this thing is."  He takes a stick and 
pokes it.  (Don't ask where he got a stick at the North Pole.  You really 
don't want to know.)  "It doesn't look natural to me eh Horn."  Horn just 
looks at him apathetically.  He walks back to the hole in the ice and drops a 
com buoy down into the water to boost his signal.  "Meteara?  Can you read 
me?  There's something up here I think you should see."

--part1_9c.245bcb38.2a8aaf71_boundary
